  "2281940": {
    "name": "The Mobius Machine",
    "steam_appid": 2281940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/500abc7aac9f0914a30e7d4ffd02cbe4.poster.avif?t=1770316952\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/500abc7aac9f0914a30e7d4ffd02cbe4.webm?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/500abc7aac9f0914a30e7d4ffd02cbe4.mp4?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Mobius Machine》是一款拥有<strong>精细 3D 画面</strong>的<strong>经典 2D 探险</strong>游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满野蛮异星生物和故障机械的交联开放式世界。在废弃设施和危险环境之间寻找路线，穿越地表和地底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无缝探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择自己的路。以自己的方式探索复杂的<strong>开放世界</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以没有加载画面的无缝方式穿越外形迥异的多样区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/f7972e4f99cd0c64862a960bb35bdb42.poster.avif?t=1770316952\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/f7972e4f99cd0c64862a960bb35bdb42.webm?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/f7972e4f99cd0c64862a960bb35bdb42.mp4?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以各种各样的致命敌人战斗：当地的动物、遭到感染的殖民者以及曾在各种设施中服役、现在却被弃置的机械等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >子弹射不停</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为<strong>手柄</strong>或<strong>键鼠</strong>控制专门设计。使用紧凑的控制系统，在向各种方向射击的同时奔跑和跳跃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时可装备 2 种武器，按需使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/813b830833b5f87b85c089051ad7552c.poster.avif?t=1770316952\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/813b830833b5f87b85c089051ad7552c.webm?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281940/extras/813b830833b5f87b85c089051ad7552c.mp4?t=1770316952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得能让你更具行动力的装备，解锁新的区域。<strong>攀爬墙壁</strong>、<strong>冲刺</strong>、<strong>潜水</strong>和<strong>滑翔</strong>，进化与世界交互的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级武器库</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集蓝图，制造全新武器和升级，从而更具效率地进行战斗。</p>",
